# Strip Jupyter Notebook outputs and execution metadata so committed .ipynb
# diffs stay limited to source changes.
#
# The pre-commit nbstripout hook handles this automatically. As a fallback for
# clones committing without pre-commit, activate the git clean filter once with:
#
#     pip install nbstripout      # if not already available
#     nbstripout --install        # configures this clone's filter.nbstripout.*
#
# Until that filter is configured locally, git ignores these lines harmlessly.
*.ipynb filter=nbstripout
*.ipynb diff=ipynb
